languages.text: И принял настоятель Гектархиус чужаков ласково, как гостей. Но и братиям своим велел осторожность блюсти.
And Prelate Hectarchius did welcome the interlopers warmly as his guests. But he did warn his brethren to keep their vigilance.

languages.text: Y el prelado Hectarchius recibió a los intrusos como si fueran invitados, aunque advirtió a sus hermanos de que no bajaran la guardia.

traits.locale_text: ... recibió a los intrusos como si fueran invitados.

languages.text: 赫克塔奇乌斯教长热情地接待了这些外来者，但也同样警告他的同伴要保持警惕。
languages.original_text: And Prelate Hectarchius did welcome the interlopers warmly as his guests. But he did warn his brethren to keep their vigilance.

languages.text: そして上級聖職者ヘクターキウスは、客人として流れ者を温かく歓迎した。ただし、仲間には警戒するようにと伝えて。
languages.original_text: And Prelate Hectarchius did welcome the interlopers warmly as his guests. But he did warn his brethren to keep their vigilance.

traits.locale_text: そして上級聖職者ヘクターキウスは、客人として流れ者を温かく歓迎した。ただし、仲間には警戒するようにと伝えて。

languages.text: Und Prälat Hectarchius begrüßte die Eindringlinge freundlich als seine Gäste. Seine Brüder ermahnte er jedoch, wachsam zu bleiben.
languages.original_text: And Prelate Hectarchius did welcome the interlopers warmly as his guests. But he did warn his brethren to keep their vigilance.

traits.locale_text: ... begrüßte die Eindringlinge freundlich als seine Gäste.

languages.text: Et le prélat Hectarchius ouvre généreusement les portes de céans aux intrus, non sans inviter ses frères à rester vigilants.

traits.locale_text: ... ouvre généreusement les portes de céans aux intrus.

languages.text: Ardından Piskopos Hectarchius, mütecavizleri sıcak bir şekilde karşıladı. Aynı zamanda yoldaşlarını dikkatli olmaları konusunda da uyardı.
